/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "SYS_UserRole" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "SYS_UserRole"
(
"UserRoleID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"UserID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"RoleID" NUMBER(10) not null,
"Level" INTEGER not null,
"OrgID" NUMBER(32),
"MallID" NUMBER(32),
"IsDefautRole" INTEGER not null,
"Remark" NVARCHAR2(500),
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
constraint PK_SYS_USERROLE primary key ("UserRoleID")
);

comment on table "SYS_UserRole" is
'用户角色关系';

comment on column "SYS_UserRole"."Level" is
'1：总部
2：大区
3：小区
4. 商场';

comment on column "SYS_UserRole"."IsDefautRole" is
'1: 是默认角色
0：不是默认角色';

comment on column "SYS_UserRole"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';

alter table "SYS_UserRole"
add constraint FK_SYS_USERROLE_2_SYS_ROLE_PK foreign key ("RoleID")
references "SYS_Role" ("RoleID");

alter table "SYS_UserRole"
add constraint FK_SYS_USERROLE_2_SYS_USER_PK foreign key ("UserID")
references "SYS_User" ("UserID");
